column1: The Catalogue of Principal Galaxies (PGC) Number
column2: Apparent Ks 20 mag/as^2 isophote magnitude adjusted for cosmological surface brightness dimming, extinction, filter redshift response, and stellar evolution, as defined by Lavaux and Hudson
column3: Velocity in Cosmic Microwave Background frame
column4: Luminosity distance (weighted average if more than one source)
